short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Prototype for automatically scheduling Duty Schedules

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The goal of this chrome extension is to help the SRAs in the Housing and Residence Life department at Virginia Tech ease the process of creating a duty schedule.
